<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.8.5">
<l>koḷḷak kuṟaiyā taviṭum paikkuḻiyil</l>
<l>taḷḷi pukappey tikolleṉ ṟataṟkañci</l>
<l>veḷḷat tiṭaippaṭ ṭanari yiṉampōlē</l>
<l>yuḷḷan tuḷaṅkā niṟpaṉū ḻimutalvā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>‘Will you dump [me], shoving [me] into a pit</l>
<l>To receive undiminishing cruelty?’ Fearing for that,</l>
<l>Like a pack of foxes caught in a flood,</l>
<l>I keep trembling [in my] heart, primeval of the cosmic dissolution.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
